quran[21]{c,v,t}:
  92,1,"By the night when it enshrouds,"
  92,2,"and by the day when it breaks in its glory,"
  92,3,"and by Him Who created the male and the female:"
  92,4,"surely your strivings are divergent.",footnotes:182743:1
  92,5,"As for him who gave out his wealth (for Allah's sake) and abstained (from disobeying Him),"
  92,6,"and affirmed the Truth of goodness:",footnotes:182744:1
  92,7,"We shall facilitate for him the Way to Bliss.",footnotes:182745:1
  92,8,"As for him who was a miser and behaved with aversion (to Allah),"
  92,9,"and denied the Truth of goodness:",footnotes:182746:1
  92,10,"We shall facilitate for him the way to Hardship,",footnotes:182747:1
  92,11,"and his wealth shall be of no avail to him when he perishes.",footnotes:182748:1
  92,12,"Surely it is for Us to show the Right Way,",footnotes:182749:1
  92,13,"and to Us belong the Next Life and the present.",footnotes:182750:1
  92,14,"I have now warned you of a Blazing Fire,"
  92,15,"where none shall burn except the most wicked,"
  92,16,"who rejected the Truth, calling it falsehood and turned his back on it."
  92,17,"But the God-fearing shall be kept away from it,"
  92,18,"the Godfearing who spends his wealth to purify himself;",footnotes:182751:1
  92,19,"not as payment for any favours that he received,"
  92,20,"but only to seek the good pleasure of his Lord Most High.",footnotes:182752:1
  92,21,"He will surely be well-pleased (with him).",footnotes:182753:1
